About the game:

Get carried away by a beautiful installment in the immensely popular Tradewinds series! Build a flotilla of ships armed with weaponry both man-made and magic, and sail off into the sky. Discover brand new ports while engaging in aerial combat with mystical sky ships! You'll sail, trade, and even battle legendary heroes like Sinbad in the mythical Far East. Enter a world of danger and intrigue with over 100 distinct tasks in Tradewinds Legends.
